🌍 Extra2Essential (E2E)
Extra2Essential (E2E) is a web-based platform designed to reduce food waste by connecting food donors with NGOs and organizations that can distribute surplus food to those in need.
The platform aims to create a bridge between restaurants, event organizers, households, and NGOs, ensuring that excess food reaches people instead of ending up as waste.
🚀 Features
🍱 Food Donation Management
Donate surplus food easily
Specify food quantity and pickup details
Real-time donation submissions
🤝 NGO Connectivity
NGOs can view available donations
Accept and manage food pickup requests
Streamlined communication between donors and NGOs
📍 Location-Based Coordination
Donation pickup location tracking
Efficient food distribution workflow
📊 Dashboard & Analytics
View donation records
Track food saved from wastage
Monitor NGO participation
📱 Responsive Design
Mobile-friendly interface
Tablet and desktop support
Optimized user experience across devices
