🎯 Problem Statement
A significant amount of edible food is wasted every day while many people struggle with food insecurity.
Extra2Essential (E2E) addresses this challenge by:
Reducing food waste
Supporting NGOs in food distribution
Encouraging community participation
Contributing towards sustainable development
🌱 SDG Alignment
This project supports:
SDG 2 – Zero Hunger
Reducing hunger through efficient food redistribution.
SDG 12 – Responsible Consumption and Production
Minimizing food waste and promoting sustainable resource utilization.
